name: FedSolutions
overview:
IT Support Service and IT Consulting

FedSolutions provides IT Management and Consulting solutions that help organizations leverage technology to achieve their business goals. Based in downtown Washington, D.C., our objective is to enable organizations to achieve their mission by successfully leveraging technology. We see IT as a strategic means for our clients to achieve a competitive advantage. Whether providing IT Support & Management services to small and midmarket organizations or expert IT Consulting services to technology professionals, we view our focus as creating smart and simple IT solutions that promote operational harmony. To learn more about our company and our passion, please visit our website at www.fedsolutions.com
